'''Tezeta Abraham''' (yavutse 15 Gashyantare 1985) numunyamideli wumutaliyani ukomoka muri [[Etiyopiya]].

== Ubuzima bwa Biografiya ==
Abrahamu yavukiye i [[Jibuti|Djibouti]] kubabyeyi ba [[Etiyopiya]]. Yimukiye hamwe n'umuryango we mu Butaliyani afite imyaka itanu. Aburahamu yarwanije umwirondoro we akiri muto, akenshi akaba ari we mukobwa wenyine wumwirabura mwishuri rye. Mu 2002, yatsindiye irushanwa rya "Miss Italy Africa" ryamufashe ku isi yimyambarire. <ref name="casolaro">https://it.businessinsider.com/tezeta-abraham-gli-italiani-sono-razzisti-ed-e-colpa-anche-della-cultura-cattolica-il-rimedio-viaggiare-e-studiare/</ref> <ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)</ref> Nkumunyamideli, yakoraga mubirango Fendi, Gianfranco Ferre, Replay, Moschino, na Jean Paul Gaultier, nabandi. <ref name="debut">https://web.archive.org/web/20151004170958/http://www.cinemafrodiscendente.com/it/--4-tezeta-a-debut-in-prime-time/</ref> Abrahamu yakiriye impamyabumenyi ye nk'umujyanama mu bukerarugendo. Yagiye muri Miss Italy mu 2010. <ref name="corriere">https://www.corriere.it/gallery/spettacoli/09-2010/missitalia/1/miss-italia-60-finaliste_d124f4ee-b5d5-11df-b220-00144f02aabe.shtml#38</ref>

Abraham yashimishijwe nisi ya sinema maze atangira kwitabira amafilime afite imyaka 18, akenshi ahabwa inshingano. Mu isuzuma yabwiwe ko ari mwiza cyane, byaramutangaje.  Muri 2012, Abraham yagize uruhare ruto muri film ''A Flat for Three'' . Ukwezi kumwe nyuma yo kugenzurwa numuyobozi Ivan Cotroneo muri 2015, Abraham yahawe umwanya ''mubiganiro bya TV È arrivata la felicità'' . <ref name="debut" /> Kuva mu 2015, yakoranye na Cotroneo kuri firime nyinshi na serivise. <ref name="casolaro" /> Muri 2017, Abraham yakinnye umunyeshuri wa kaminuza ashishikajwe nubuzima bwa Lord Byron na Mary Shelley, mubutaliyani muri film ngufi ''L'ultima rima'' . <ref>https://ricerca.gelocal.it/mattinopadova/archivio/mattinopadova/2018/03/20/padova-l-ultima-rima-di-fracanzani-55.html</ref> Yakinnye umubyeyi muri firime ngufi ya 2018 ''La festa più bellissima'' . Muri 2019, Abraham yafashije gutangiza iserukiramuco rya Filime rya MiWorld. <ref>http://www.cinemafrica.org/spip.php?article1772</ref>

Aburahamu afite umuhungu. Yamaganaga ivanguramoko mu Butaliyani, avuga ko abirabura baba ku nkengero za sosiyete ari umuco w’Abagatolika. Abrahamu kandi ateza imbere ingendo nkinzira yo gufungura ibitekerezo mumico mishya.  Ubu atuye i [[Roma]] . 

